🎗️Hyper Text Markup Language (HTTP).
Basically defines the layout,it contains lots of tags.

✅Creating a HTML file
1.create a folder and creare a file name.html
2.procced with syntax
3.save the file
4.Open the file in a browser 
5.the browser will render the html syntax and present it.

✅ Sample code :

<!DOCTYPE html>  
    <html lang="en">
        <head>
    <title>E Marketplace</title>
        </head>
        <body>
            <h1>
                Welcome to E-marketplace
            </h1>
            <h2>
                Introduction
            </h2>
            <p>
                This is an <b> online market place</b> where costumers can directly buy<i> goods </i><u>from farmersmaking organic goods</u> and woth the cost.
            </p>
    
        </body>
    </html>
    
    This snippet contins basics tags like <h>,<p>,<i>,<b>,<u>. 
    snippet code is used to create a e-market place as title and a  welcome text in <h1> to diffrentiate the size from <h2>.
    paragraph <p> .
